<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Análisis de Correos | DAAT</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/feather-icons/4.29.0/feather.min.js" integrity="sha512-Kolh2UJkNnRbl+uKf1nwZbmhICd5jPuuhSXsXmqGfZzPRv7fi8V+fhnjWqMEOd4rbyXZ1WOGcPC1nCzWYmGiVQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-slate-100 font-inter">
    <div id="toast-container" class="fixed right-5 top-5 z-50 space-y-3"></div>
    <div class="flex min-h-screen">
      <%- include('partials/sidebar', { user, title }) %>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <%- include('partials/header', { user, title }) %>
        <main class="p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="grid gap-6 xl:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr]">
            <section class="space-y-6 rounded-[32px] border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/95 p-6 shadow-glow">
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-400">Módulo principal</p>
                <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-white">Análisis de Correos</h2>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-400">Introduce los detalles del correo sospechoso y recibe un reporte de riesgo basado en Gemini.</p>
              </div>

              <form id="analysisForm" class="space-y-5">
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm text-slate-300">Remitente</label>
                  <input type="text" name="sender" required class="mt-2 w-full rounded-3xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-950 px-4 py-3 text-white outline-none focus:border-cyan-400" placeholder="soporte@empresa.com" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm text-slate-300">Asunto</label>
                  <input type="text" name="subject" required class="mt-2 w-full rounded-3xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-950 px-4 py-3 text-white outline-none focus:border-cyan-400" placeholder="Actualiza tu cuenta ahora" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm text-slate-300">Contenido del correo</label>
                  <textarea name="content" rows="6" required class="mt-2 w-full rounded-3xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-950 px-4 py-3 text-white outline-none focus:border-cyan-400" placeholder="Hola, necesitamos verificar tu cuenta..." ></textarea>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm text-slate-300">URLs opcionales</label>
                  <input type="text" name="urls" class="mt-2 w-full rounded-3xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-950 px-4 py-3 text-white outline-none focus:border-cyan-400" placeholder="https://login-falso.example" />
                </div>
                <button id="analyzeButton" type="submit" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-3xl bg-cyan-500 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 transition hover:bg-cyan-400">
                  <span>Analizar correo</span>
                  <i data-feather="search" class="h-4 w-4"></i>
                </button>
              </form>

              <div id="analysisCard" class="hidden rounded-[32px] border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/90 p-6" data-testid="result-card">
                <div class="mb-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">Resultado IA</p>
                    <h3 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Reporte de detección</h3>
                  </div>
                  <span id="riskBadge" class="rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Confianza</p>
                    <div class="mt-3 h-4 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-slate-800">
                      <div id="confidenceBar" class="h-full rounded-full bg-cyan-400" style="width:0%"></div>
                    </div>
                    <p id="confidenceLabel" class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300"></p>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Indicadores detectados</p>
                    <div id="threatTags" class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Explicación</p>
                    <p id="explanationText" class="mt-2 rounded-3xl bg-slate-900/80 p-4 text-slate-200"></p>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Recomendación</p>
                    <p id="recommendationText" class="mt-2 rounded-3xl bg-slate-900/80 p-4 text-slate-200"></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <aside class="space-y-6">
              <div class="rounded-[32px] border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/95 p-6 shadow-glow">
                <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-400">Últimas acciones</p>
                <p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">Consulta el historial para ver el desempeño de análisis anteriores.</p>
                <a href="/analysis/history" class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-3xl bg-slate-950/90 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-slate-800">
                  Ver historial
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-[32px] border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/95 p-6 shadow-glow">
                <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">Indicadores clave</p>
                <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-slate-300">
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400"></span> Phishing y spoofing</li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400"></span> Ingeniería social</li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-rose-400"></span> Tono urgente</li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span> URLs sospechosas</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </main>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script>feather.replace();</script>
    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/analysis.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
